# Open Grant Proposal: `Distributed Incentives for Hospitality Review`

**Distributed Incentives for Hospitality Review**

**Proposal Category:** `app-dev`

**Proposer:** `3Labs`

**Do you agree to open source all work you do on behalf of this RFP and dual-license under MIT and APACHE2 licenses?:** "Yes" 

# Project Description

A web app for hospitality reviews in which customer would be incentivized for their honest review. It would be using Filecoin to create a distributed trusted system. Hedera would be used for incentives.

## Value

Customers will be incentivized for giving an honest and trusted review. Hedera 

## Deliverables

A web app with reviews on hospitality. 

## Development Roadmap

Sep - Dec 2021: Review incentive module development - 3 developers (~ USD 9.000)
Jan - Jun 2022: Web app integration - 7 developers (~ USD 21.000)

## Total Budget Requested

USD 30.000. + $ 5000 FIL

## Maintenance and Upgrade Plans

API development so that relevant industries may utilize the app.

# Team

